# Description
# -----------
#
#  Completion script for composer (https://getcomposer.org/).
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Authors
# -------
#
#  * Daniel Gomes (me@danielcsgomes.com)
#  * Valerii Hiora (https://github.com/vhbit)
#  * loranger (https://github.com/loranger)
